{"word":"ἐπιδίζημαι","slug":"ἐπιδίζημαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιδίζημαι</b></el> <el><b>ἐπιδίζομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to inquire besides, to go on to inquire</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to seek for</i> or <i>demand besides</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; so, <el>ἐπιδίζομαι</el>, <b><a href='S:Moschus'>Mosch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}